@node "about" "About RentSpace"

Name      : Rent Space
Copyright : ©1995 PalaceSoft
BB System : MAX'sBBS
Function  : To create an ANSI Advertisement
Version   : v2.2

There are 2 door programs contained in this archive,

RentSpace        <-- Main Editor and file creator
RentSpaceV       <-- Advert/file Displayer

The first one creates the needed files and is also the main editor
the second one is the Displayer or Viewer thus the V
